snippet.title: Lieve Oma - trailer
snippet.description:
Download the game here!
https://vltmn.itch.io/lieve-oma

It's the season for penny buns, Grandma forced you to come along a bit. But deep down you know it'll do you good and take your mind off of things.
Lieve Oma is a game about going for a walk with your grandmother, released April 5th, 2016.
follow me on twitter https://twitter.com/FlorianVltmn/
